messages.title: 3 great reasons to vote for Millicent Scott
messages.content: As a local Millicent is as concerned as you are about local, as well as national and international issues. Millicent represents a fresh start for Hammersmith, championing green issues, youth engagement and gender equality. Having worked the charity, public and private sectors, Millicent brings real-world experience to politics and can use that knowledge to drive social justice forwards.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Concerned about a breadth of issues from local to international.
